The paper discusses the generalization error of convolutional neural networks, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper specifically focuses on convolutional neural networks, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.CL.
